ibrix.name: ibrix

revisions.description: Corrected soltionSerialNumber -> solutionSerialNumber at Object definition
Corrected Organization & contact information Product version to which this MIB belongs to is mentioned in the description above
Event Index added to Event variable bindings

Added new SolutionInformation Group for the purposes of PhoneHome Added new HardwareInformation Table for enumerating the underlying hardware Changed fields eventOrigin, eventData1 and eventData2 to eventUUID, eventSolutionSerialNumber and eventSolutionProductNumber in eventEntry Added new field eventFRU to eventEntry Updated description of eventText

Added new enumerations to eventType for 4.2 release Added warn enumeration to eventSeverity object Added new eventText object to contain the event descriptive text that combines eventDescription, eventOrigin, eventData1, eventData2 into one eventOrigin changed to obsolete eventData1 and eventData2 changed to obsolete
Adding new segment and job information
Initial version of the IBRIX MIB module
